{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-js","path":"/post/whatsapp-tak-bisa-digunakan-di-ponsel-tua/","result":{"data":{"wordpressPost":{"title":"WhatsApp Tak Bisa Lagi Digunakan Di Ponsel Tua","content":"<p>WhatsApp baru saja mengumumkan bahwa aplikasi ini akan berhenti beroperasi di beberapa smartphone, seperti iPhone dan Android. Meski beritanya mendadak, mereka membuat kebijakan ini secara mutlak di situs resmi <a href=\"https://faq.whatsapp.com/en/bb/26000006/\">mereka</a>. Disana tertulis beberapa sistem operasi yang tidak bisa mendukung penggunaan aplikasi WhatsApp, yaitu:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Android versi dibawah dari Gingerbead (2.3.3)</li>\n<li>Windows Phone 8.0 dan versi sebelumnya</li>\n<li>iPhone 3GS/iOS 6</li>\n<li>Nokia Symbian S60</li>\n<li>BlackBerry OS dan BlackBerry 10</li>\n</ul>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_48667\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-48667\" data-attachment-id=\"48667\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/whatsapp-tak-bisa-digunakan-di-ponsel-tua/attachment/01-whatsapp-discontinue/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/01-whatsapp-discontinue.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"01-whatsapp discontinue\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/01-whatsapp-discontinue-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/01-whatsapp-discontinue.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-48667\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/01-whatsapp-discontinue.jpg\" alt=\"Android Gingerbead tidak akan mendukung aplikasi WhatsApp dalam waktu dekat. (Sumber: itmagazine)\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/01-whatsapp-discontinue.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/01-whatsapp-discontinue-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-48667\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Android Gingerbead tidak akan mendukung aplikasi WhatsApp dalam waktu dekat. (Sumber: itmagazine)</p></div></p>\n<p>Dalam beberapa tahun ini, aplikasi WhatsApp sudah banyak digunakan oleh penduduk Indonesia. Selain untuk mengirim pesan dan melakukan panggilan, aplikasi ini juga sebagai media untuk berkumpul dengan membuat grup chat, mulai dari teman sekolah, pekerjaan, melakukan jual-beli, keluarga dan paling yang paling terkenal adalah grup WhatsApp emak-emak/ibu-ibu maupun bapak-bapak.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_48668\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-48668\" data-attachment-id=\"48668\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/whatsapp-tak-bisa-digunakan-di-ponsel-tua/attachment/02-whatsapp-discontinue/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/02-whatsapp-discontinue.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"02-whatsapp-discontinue\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/02-whatsapp-discontinue-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/02-whatsapp-discontinue.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-48668\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/02-whatsapp-discontinue.jpg\" alt=\"40% warga Indonesia menggunakan aplikasi Whatsapp (Sumber: Statista)\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/02-whatsapp-discontinue.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/02-whatsapp-discontinue-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-48668\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">40% warga Indonesia menggunakan aplikasi Whatsapp (Sumber: Statista)</p></div></p>\n<p>Para pengguna WhatsApp yang masih menggunakan OS (Operating System) Gingerbead dan versi sebelumnya diharapkan untuk segera melakukan update OS. Jika sudah tidak bisa melakukan update sebaiknya membeli smartphone baru agar bisa menggunakan aplikasi ini. Hal ini juga berlaku untuk smartphone yang memiliki OS dibawah versi yang sudah disebutkan sebelumnya.</p>\n<p>WhatsApp menyarankan para pengguna untuk menggunakan OS sebagai berikut:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Android dengan OS diatas versi 4.0</li>\n<li>iPhone dengan iOS versi 8 dan diatasnya</li>\n<li>Windows Phone 8.1 dan versi diatasnya</li>\n</ul>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_48669\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-48669\" data-attachment-id=\"48669\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/whatsapp-tak-bisa-digunakan-di-ponsel-tua/attachment/03-whatsapp-discontinue/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/03-whatsapp-discontinue.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"03-whatsapp-discontinue\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/03-whatsapp-discontinue-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/03-whatsapp-discontinue.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-48669\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/03-whatsapp-discontinue.jpg\" alt=\"Windows Phone 8.1 masih bisa menggunakan WhatsApp sampai saat ini. (Sumber: betanews)\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/03-whatsapp-discontinue.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/03-whatsapp-discontinue-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-48669\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Windows Phone 8.1 masih bisa menggunakan WhatsApp sampai saat ini. (Sumber: betanews)</p></div></p>\n<p>Apabila kalian masih menggunakan OS lama seperti yang dijelaskan sebelumnya, WhatsApp akan memberikan batas waktu tertentu, yaitu:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Nokia S40 sampai 31 December 2018</li>\n<li>Android versions 2.3.7 dan versi dibawahnya sampai 1 Februari 2020</li>\n<li>iOS 7 dan versi dibawahnya sampai 1 February 2020</li>\n</ul>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_48670\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-48670\" data-attachment-id=\"48670\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/whatsapp-tak-bisa-digunakan-di-ponsel-tua/attachment/04-whatsapp-discontinue/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/04-whatsapp-discontinue.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"04-whatsapp-discontinue\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/04-whatsapp-discontinue-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/04-whatsapp-discontinue.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-48670\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/04-whatsapp-discontinue.jpg\" alt=\"Ini menjadi kabar buruk buat pengguna Nokia S40. (Sumber: neurogadget)\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/04-whatsapp-discontinue.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/04-whatsapp-discontinue-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-48670\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Ini menjadi kabar buruk buat pengguna Nokia S40. (Sumber: neurogadget)</p></div></p>\n<p>Para pengguna OS versi lama tidak bisa lagi membuat akun WhatsApp yang baru, tapi mereka masih bisa menggunakan aplikasi tersebut sampai batas waktu yang sudah diberikan. Aplikasi ini bisa saja tiba tiba berhenti beroperasi tanpa pemberitahuan ataupun lebih cepat dari batas waktunya. Seperti yang telah terjadi pada Blackberry OS, Blackberry 10, dan Windows Phone 8.0 dan versi sebelumnya.</p>\n<p>Seperti yang kalian ketahui, WhatsApp memiliki fitur back up chat history apabila kita memindahkan akun dari satu smartphone ke smartphone lain. Tapi fitur ini tidak akan berfungsi apabila back up akun akan dipindahkan ke platform yang berbeda, seperti android ke iPhone atau sebaliknya. Mereka mengatakan bahwa “Untuk saat ini tidak ada option melakukan transfer chat history pada akun diantara platform yang berbeda. Tetapi, kami mengusahakan back up chat history akun pengguna dikirim melalui email.”</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_48671\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-48671\" data-attachment-id=\"48671\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/whatsapp-tak-bisa-digunakan-di-ponsel-tua/attachment/05-whatsapp-discontinue/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/05-whatsapp-discontinue.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"05-whatsapp-discontinue\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/05-whatsapp-discontinue-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/05-whatsapp-discontinue.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-48671\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/05-whatsapp-discontinue.jpg\" alt=\"Jan Koum, salah satu pendiri aplikasi WhatsApp. (Sumber: quoracdn)\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/05-whatsapp-discontinue.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/05-whatsapp-discontinue-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-48671\" class=\"wp-caption-text\"><a href=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/boss-whatsapp-hengkang-dari-facebook/\">Jan Koum</a>, salah satu pendiri aplikasi WhatsApp. (Sumber: quoracdn)</p></div></p>\n<p>Jadi sekarang sudah saatnya mengupdate OS kalian agar bisa menggunakan aplikasi WhatsApp. Beritahukan juga berita ini kepada teman, sahabat, dan keluarga kalian. Dan jangan lupa back up terlebih dahulu chat history kalian apabila terdapat file-file penting didalamnya.</p>\n"}},"pageContext":{"isCreatedByStatefulCreatePages":false,"id":"363ad562-ad0e-5270-8c68-55c310aa245d"}}}